[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "冬日的午后，我正独自待在作战指挥室中，批阅着积压的文件。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……还剩二十五份啊，应该能在预计的两个小时里弄完。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "粗略估计了一下文件的量级后，我做出了乐观的估计。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "毕竟这批阅文件的两小时也是我从训练、陪伴队员以及陪伴队员训练的时间中挤出来的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "以现在海姆达尔的人数来说，腾出这两小时堪称不易。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好在我现在有两个可靠的助手——卡罗琳和露娜，她们会事先帮我解决掉大部分的文件，大大减轻了我的负担。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "摇了摇头，将脑中的思绪放下后，我的目光重新回到了面前的终端上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两小时后……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呼，完工。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我揉了揉微微发酸的眼睛，顺手关掉了终端。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在这时，指挥室外忽然传来了门铃声，紧接着，门外传来了熟悉的声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，请问我可以进去吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "进来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "指挥室的门应声而开，一只手拿着纸质文件、一只手端着马克杯的少女随即走了进来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "工作辛苦了，分析员，我为您泡了咖啡。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谢了，露娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "咖啡的香气冲淡了工作后的疲惫，抿了几口之后，我重新抬起头看向露娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你手上的是？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我撰写的活动草案。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她将那份纸质文件递给了我。厚厚的纸张微微发热，看起来是刚刚被打印出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“关于筹备星祈节庆典的计划书”……啊，星祈节快到了啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看到了文件的标题，我方才想起了这件事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "每年的第一天，便是被称作星祈节的节日。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这个节日在成年病时代被设立，人们在这一天庆祝孩童们茁壮长大，并为新一年的健康平安而祈福。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "成年病危机得到解决后，星祈节的传统保留了下来，世界各地的人们几乎都会在这一天举办新年庆典活动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "庆典的内容，则包括布置星祈树，准备礼物，许下愿望等等。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这么说来，自从我从槲寄生空间站返回后，就投身于各种各样的事情中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "往年的星祈节，我都不在公司，因此也没有进行庆祝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "数据表明，定期举办庆典，能显著提升工作效率，对于公司和员工很有帮助。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "另外，我也希望您能够借此机会休息放松几天。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她忽然凑近了些，用扑闪扑闪的眼睛注视着我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "您这几天一直在熬夜吧，眼睛里已经有血丝了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在庆典的这段时间里，还请照顾好自己的身体。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "至于工作的事情，还请放心交给我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "您知道的，我实际上并不需要现在这么多的休息时间……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "露娜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我打断了她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我知道你可以不眠不休地工作很长时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但还记得，我之前是怎么和你说的吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯……从卫城学院回来后，您告诉我，我应该融入到公司的工作和生活中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要正常吃饭、睡觉，定时休息娱乐，不能没完没了地工作。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我点了点头，将露娜拉到我的身边坐下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之所以这么要求她，是因为露娜在回公司以后立刻进入了工作狂状态，一连高负荷工作了好几天。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不免怀疑起，是不是我过去的工作模式给她留下了不好的习惯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然是星祈节庆典，那大家都应该一起庆祝。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在筹备阶段，我们一起努力，然后在庆典当天好好放松吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好的，我明白了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她认真地点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我想和分析员一起过星祈节，在此之前，我会去做好准备的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "遇到什么问题的话，随时告诉我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我伸出手揉了揉她的头，她则小心翼翼地，将脑袋靠在了我的肩上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一丝若有若无的白色蒸汽似乎从她的头顶上冒出，先前我便发现，露娜害羞的时候便会出现这样可爱的反应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "露娜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你想要什么星祈节礼物呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "礼物的话……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我思索起有什么是我需要，而露娜准备起来不至于太费劲的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，有件事情……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这时，指挥室的门忽然打开，身形小巧的情报官随即出现在了门口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的手中捧着发亮的终端，脸上带着浅笑，像是取得了什么成果，迫不及待地想要和我分享。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而在看到了坐在我身边的露娜后，卡罗琳忽然止住了话头，转而换上了平时那副严肃的表情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "咳咳……露娜小姐也在啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么了，卡罗琳？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没什么，就是那个……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "低头快速滑动了几下终端，又犹豫了片刻后，卡罗琳方才继续说了下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就是今年的星祈节快到了，这次你难得留在公司，我想给你……咳咳，我是说，我筹划了一个星祈节庆典，可以让大家一起参与。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她说完后，便将终端递了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我大致做了个方案，如果你没问题的话，我们很快就能开工。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的心中忽然升起了一丝不妙的预感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "果然，快速扫视了卡罗琳给出的方案后，我的预感得到了验证。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这份方案很完美，充分考虑到了时间成本和庆典效果。唯一的问题是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "关于星祈节庆典的方案，我几分钟前才刚刚看过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你觉得怎么样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见我没有第一时间给出反应，卡罗琳略带紧张地发出了疑问。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我觉得很好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
